  "ai_usage": "Use for product/hardware brands, audio apps, or nostalgic flair. Materials are pure CSS: brushed metal = layered repeating-linear-gradient + overall linear-gradient; bevels = paired inset light/dark box-shadows; gloss = a top white-to-transparent overlay; the knob = radial gradients with a notch. Keep all controls real <button>s with aria-labels and a reduced-motion guard on the equalizer.",
  "path": "effects/website-templates/skeuomorphic-revival.html",
  "source": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n<title>Skeuomorphic Revival — Music Player</title>\n<script type=\"application/json\" id=\"effect-meta\">\n{\n  \"id\": \"skeuomorphic-revival\",\n  \"title\": \"Skeuomorphic Revival — Music Player\",\n  \"summary\": \"Tactile, realistic UI: a brushed-metal music player with a glossy LCD, embossed buttons, and a chunky knob — skeuomorphism, reborn.\",\n  \"description\": \"Skeuomorphism is making a 2026 comeback as a reaction to flatness — realistic materials rendered purely in CSS. This landing showcases a hi-fi music player 'device': brushed-metal body, inset glossy screen, beveled play/skip buttons, an LED, and a metallic volume knob, beside a product pitch.\",\n  \"theme\": \"website-templates\",\n  \"categories\": [\"template\", \"landing\", \"product\"],\n  \"tags\": [\"skeuomorphism\", \"tactile\", \"realistic\", \"material\", \"device\", \"music\", \"full-page\"],\n  \"tech\": [\"html\", \"css\", \"js\"],\n  \"era\": \"2020s\",\n  \"difficulty\": \"advanced\",\n  \"dependencies\": [],\n  \"browser_support\": \"All modern browsers (layered gradients + box-shadows).\",\n  \"performance_notes\": \"All materials are CSS — layered linear/radial gradients and multi-layer box-shadows (inset bevels + drop shadows). No images. A small JS play toggle animates the equalizer.\",\n  \"accessibility_notes\": \"Controls are real buttons with aria-labels/aria-pressed; the screen text is real; focus-visible rings; equalizer bars stop under reduced-motion.\",\n  \"customization\": [\n    { \"name\": \"metal gradients\", \"description\": \"Body/knob brushed-metal stops\", \"default\": \"cool grey\" },\n    { \"name\": \"--led\", \"description\": \"LED / accent color\", \"default\": \"#46e0a0\" }\n  ],\n  \"variations\": [\"Wood/leather material set\", \"Dark titanium finish\", \"A 'thermostat' or 'camera' device instead\"],\n  \"related\": [\"press-3d-button\",\"clay-app\"],\n  \"ai_usage\": \"Use for product/hardware brands, audio apps, or nostalgic flair. Materials are pure CSS: brushed metal = layered repeating-linear-gradient + overall linear-gradient; bevels = paired inset light/dark box-shadows; gloss = a top white-to-transparent overlay; the knob = radial gradients with a notch. Keep all controls real <button>s with aria-labels and a reduced-motion guard on the equalizer.\"\n}\n</script>\n<style>\n  :root{--led:#46e0a0;}\n  *{box-sizing:border-box}\n  body{margin:0;min-height:100vh;font-family:\"Helvetica Neue\",system-ui,sans-serif;color:#2a2e36;\n    background:linear-gradient(160deg,#cdd3db,#aeb6c2);display:grid;place-items:center;padding:2.5rem 1.2rem}\n  .stage{max-width:1000px;width:100%;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:3rem;align-items:center}\n  .pitch .badge{display:inline-block;background:#fff;border-radius:999px;padding:.35rem .9rem;font-size:.8rem;color:#5a6270;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.15),inset 0 1px 0 #fff}\n  .pitch h1{font-size:clamp(2.2rem,5vw,3.6rem);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.05;margin:1rem 0 .6rem;\n    color:#2a2e36;text-shadow:0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.6)}\n  .pitch p{color:#525a68;font-size:1.12rem;max-width:40ch}\n  .metal-btn{display:inline-block;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-weight:700;color:#33383f;padding:.85rem 1.6rem;border-radius:12px;margin-top:1rem;\n    background:linear-gradient(#fdfefe,#c3cad4);box-shadow:0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.25),inset 0 1px 0 #fff,inset 0 -2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.12)}\n  .metal-btn:active{box-shadow:inset 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,.3)}\n  .metal-btn:focus-visible{outline:3px solid #5b8cff;outline-offset:3px}\n  /* device */\n  .device{justify-self:center;width:320px;border-radius:34px;padding:24px;\n    background:linear-gradient(145deg,#eef1f5,#aab2bf);\n    box-shadow:0 30px 60px rgba(40,50,70,.45),inset 0 2px 3px rgba(255,255,255,.9),inset 0 -4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.25)}\n  .brushed{border-radius:22px;padding:20px;background:\n    repeating-linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,.5) 0 1px,rgba(0,0,0,.04) 1px 2px),linear-gradient(160deg,#dfe4ea,#b8c0cc);\n    box-shadow:inset 0 2px 4px rgba(255,255,255,.7),inset 0 -3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.2)}\n  .screen{border-radius:14px;padding:1rem 1.1rem;color:#063b2b;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\n    background:linear-gradient(160deg,#9be7c4,#5cc79c);\n    box-shadow:inset 0 3px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.35),inset 0 -1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.4),0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.6)}\n  .screen::after{content:\"\";position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.45),transparent 45%);pointer-events:none}\n  .screen .now{font-size:.7rem;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;opacity:.7}\n  .screen .track{font-weight:800;font-size:1.15rem;margin:.1rem 0}\n  .eq{display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:3px;height:26px;margin-top:.4rem}\n  .eq i{width:4px;background:#063b2b;border-radius:2px;height:30%}\n  .device.playing .eq i{animation:eq .8s ease-in-out infinite alternate}\n  .device.playing .eq i:nth-child(2){animation-delay:.1s}.device.playing .eq i:nth-child(3){animation-delay:.2s}\n  .device.playing .eq i:nth-child(4){animation-delay:.15s}.device.playing .eq i:nth-child(5){animation-delay:.25s}\n  @keyframes eq{to{height:100%}}\n  .controls{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-top:1.2rem}\n  .round{width:54px;height:54px;border-radius:50%;border:none;cursor:pointer;color:#33383f;font-size:1.1rem;display:grid;place-items:center;\n    background:linear-gradient(#fdfefe,#c3cad4);box-shadow:0 3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.3),inset 0 1px 0 #fff,inset 0 -2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,.15)}\n  .round:active{box-shadow:inset 0 3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.3)}\n  .round.play{width:68px;height:68px;font-size:1.4rem;color:#0a6b4c;background:linear-gradient(#eafff6,#aee2cd)}\n  .round:focus-visible{outline:3px solid #5b8cff;outline-offset:3px}\n  .knob{width:64px;height:64px;border-radius:50%;position:relative;\n    background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 40%,#fbfdff,#aab2bf 60%,#8b94a3);\n    box-shadow:0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.35),inset 0 2px 3px rgba(255,255,255,.9),inset 0 -3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.25)}\n  .knob::after{content:\"\";position:absolute;left:50%;top:8px;width:4px;height:16px;background:#5a6270;border-radius:2px;transform:translateX(-50%)}\n  .led{width:12px;height:12px;border-radius:50%;background:radial-gradient(circle at 35% 35%,#bfffe4,var(--led));box-shadow:0 0 10px var(--led),inset 0 -2px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.3)}\n  .topbar{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:14px;color:#5a6270;font-size:.7rem;letter-spacing:.1em}\n  @media(max-width:820px){.stage{grid-template-columns:1fr;text-align:center}.pitch p{margin-inline:auto}}\n  @media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.device.playing .eq i{animation:none;height:70%}}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <main class=\"stage\">\n    <div class=\"pitch\">\n      <span class=\"badge\">◉ The Æther One · hi-fi player</span>\n      <h1>Music you can feel under your thumb.</h1>\n      <p>Real buttons. Real weight. A warm, tactile player for people who miss the click. Lossless audio, 40-hour battery, machined aluminum.</p>\n      <button class=\"metal-btn\">Pre-order — $299</button>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"device\" id=\"device\">\n      <div class=\"brushed\">\n        <div class=\"topbar\"><span>ÆTHER</span><span class=\"led\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></div>\n        <div class=\"screen\">\n          <div class=\"now\">Now playing</div>\n          <div class=\"track\">Afterglow — Remy Fields</div>\n          <div class=\"eq\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"controls\">\n          <button class=\"round\" aria-label=\"Previous track\">⏮</button>\n          <button class=\"round play\" id=\"play\" aria-label=\"Play\" aria-pressed=\"false\">▶</button>\n          <button class=\"round\" aria-label=\"Next track\">⏭</button>\n          <div class=\"knob\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Volume knob\"></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </main>\n  <script>\n    var device=document.getElementById('device'),play=document.getElementById('play');\n    play.addEventListener('click',function(){\n      var on=device.classList.toggle('playing');\n      play.textContent=on?'⏸':'▶'; play.setAttribute('aria-pressed',on); play.setAttribute('aria-label',on?'Pause':'Play');\n    });\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
}
